ched to the pendulum just above the table. Another weight of about 10 lb. is attached as shown at H. A pedestal, J}}{\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\fs20\fs20{\charscalex82 , }{\charscalex108 provides a means of sup\-port for the stylus. The stylus arm should have pin-point bearings, to prevent any side motion. }}
