\par {\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 The above-mentioned instruments have no patents on them, and anyone is at liberty to build and use them. The writer does not claim to be the origi\-nator, but simply illustrates the above to show that, after all, wireless is very simple when it is once unde
