 It will run as large a lamp a 3-1/2}{\charscalex74  }{\charscalex106 volts, 1 cp., for some time very satisfactorily. More than one lamp can be run by connect\-ing the bulbs in parallel, as indicated by Fig. }{\charscalex119 1, }{\charscalex106 which shows the special bat\-tery with 3 dry cells in the case, and the 2 bindi
