ut 7 in. or 8 in. in length, as the maker prefers, and bundled to a diameter of 7/8}}{\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\fs20\fs20{\f4  }{\charscalex107 in. The wires may be straightened by roll\-ing two or three at a time between two pieces of hard wood. If the amateur has difficulty in procuring this wire, the entire core 
