\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi201\rtlch\af0\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af0\afs24\langfe1033\loch\fs24\lang1033{\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0\fs20{\charscalex109 Wireless messages have been re\-ceived at Washington, D.C.}}{\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\fs20\fs20{\charscalex90\f4 , }{\charscalex109 from Key West, Florida, a distance of 900 miles, through a receiving instrument in which two pieces of quartz of different composition were used on the elec\-trodes. In making an instrument of this 
