\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af0\afs24\langfe1033\loch\fs24\lang1033{\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0\fs20{\charscalex109 to collecting combs attached to dis\-charging rods. The glass selected for the plates must be clear white glass, free from wrinkles, and of a uniform thickness. Two plates are necessary to make this machine, and the glass should be of sufficient size to cut
