\par {\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 When the paraffin has cooled suffi\-ciently the outlines of the photograph must be drawn upon its surface. There are three ways of doing this:  First, the photograph can be traced on tissue paper and then retraced on the paraffin surface. The exact outlines
