d ad\-justed with screws. The apparatus is started by clamping the rubber tube tightly and then exhausting the air in the siphon tube, then placing the end in the upper reservoir and releasing the clamp until the water begins to drop. If the reservoir is ke
pt filled from the tank, the device will work for an indefinite time. --Contributed by John T. Dunlop, Shettleston, Scotland. }
