ughly dry, remove all the surplus with a sharp knife. Sheets of tinfoil are secured for covering the blade. Cut two strips of tinfoil, one about 1/2}{\charscalex80\i  }{\charscalex106 in. wider than the blade and the other 1/4}{\charscalex55\f4  }{\charscalex106 in. narrower. Quickly cover one side of the blade with a thin co
