\par {\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 A very handsome weapon is the Ger\-man halberd of the sixteenth century which is shown in Fig. 7. The entire length is about 6-1/2 ft., with a round wooden handle fitted at the lower end with a steel ornament. The length of the spear point to the lower end 
