c\-tion coil was through connected with these wires and about six dry batteries were used to run the induction coil whenever a push button was manipulated. }}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi270\rtlch\af0\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af0\afs24\langfe1033\loch\fs24\lang1033{\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0\fs20{\charscalex106 It is quite evident that when a rat put its two fore feet on the edge of the pan in order to eat the mush which it contained, that an electrical connection would be made through the body of the rat, and when we pushed the button up in the shop the rat woul
