cutting edge to penetrate far enough to sever the piece. Bending cold with a wooden form is done as in Fig. }{\charscalex108 18. }{\charscalex105 The wooden form is marked P and is about 8 in. wide and 7 in. high, forming a one-sided oval shape. There is a pin R set into the base board of 
