 As the jars have the same style top they can be used interchangeably with one mouth\-piece. }
\par {\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 The mouthpiece is made of a round\- neck bottle of which the glass is color\-less and rather thin. If the neck of the bottle is cut at the right point, it makes a glass funnel that will just fit into the fruit jar. The funnel forms the mouth of the trap. Put
