\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\charscalex109{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af0\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af0\afs20\langfe1033\loch\fs20\lang1033 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\charscalex109{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi201\rtlch\af0\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af0\afs20\langfe1033\loch\fs20\lang1033 {\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 A chair more than a hundred years old came to me by inheritance. It was originally painted green and had been given two coats of dark paint or var\-nish within the last 30 years. Desiring to improve the appearance of the relic, I decided to remove the paint
