\par {\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 The machine should have a speed that will cause the pen to move over the paper at the same rate as in ordi\-nary writing. The ink should flow freely from the pen as it passes over the paper. A very fine pen may be necessary to prevent the lines from running
